PrecisCUSTOMS BONDED WAREHOUSES REGULATIONS which replace the regulations made under the Customs Act, enhance the extent to which goods may be manipulated, altered or combined with other goods, and increase the length of time that goods may be left in a bonded warehouse to reflect the other time limits of the duty deferral program.
